This Magento module informs the user if a transaction failed.

Installation:
- Copy all files and folders into your Magento Installation

Configuration:
- Edit the template "Transaktion fehlgeschlagen Kundeninformation" under System/Transaction Emails
- You can use the variables {{var customer}} as Name, {{var dateAndTime}}, 
{{var reason}}, {{var currency}}, {{var couponCode}}, {{var couponValue}}
- Choose the template under System/Configuration/Checkout/Payment failed
- In the same section you can decide if you want to send a coupon to the customer